WEBVTT

00:03.606 --> 00:05.564
Who's that woman? Clarity Winlove.

00:05.566 --> 00:07.621
Say she was a healer, helped
women who wanted to conceive.

00:07.622 --> 00:10.533
I want your baby, Nathan Appleby.

00:10.534 --> 00:13.530
You will reap what has been sown.

00:14.546 --> 00:15.597
Nathan.

00:15.598 --> 00:18.537
This isn't a blessing,
nor is it a curse.

00:18.538 --> 00:20.514
I'm not pregnant. I think you are.

00:20.613 --> 00:23.564
One night in Shepzoy, I saw a woman.

00:23.565 --> 00:25.600
Gabriel drew a picture
of a woman with a book

00:25.601 --> 00:27.624
and so did Harriet.

00:27.625 --> 00:31.624
I heard Gabriel's voice.
I am sure of it.

00:31.625 --> 00:34.581
There's something here,
something bad.

00:37.541 --> 00:41.541
Never return to my land.
You are banished, Jack.

